{"word":"H8471 - תַּחְפַּנְחֵס - Tachpanchêç - takh-pan-khace' - Tahapanes","slug":"H8471","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תַּחְפַּנְחֵס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Tachpanchêç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>takh-pan-khace'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Tahapanes"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D7;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05E1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D7;&#x05E4;&#x05E0;&#x05D7;&#x05E1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05D7;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E0;&#x05D7;&#x05E1;</b><sup></bdo>o</sup> - <b>tachpanche&#x0302;s  t<sup>e</sup>chaphn<sup>e</sup>che&#x0302;s  tachp<sup>e</sup>ne&#x0302;s</b> - <i>takh-pan-khace' tekh-af-nekh-ace' (etc.)<p/></i>(The second form used in <a href='B:330 30:18'>Eze 30:18</a>); (the third form used in <a href='B:300 2:16'>Jer 2:16</a>); of Egyptian derivation; <i>Tachpanches</i>, <i>Techaphneches</i> or <i>Tachpenes</i>, a place in Egypt: - Tahapanes, Tahpanhes, Tehaphnehes."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8456\">H8456</a>, <a href=\"#/H8472\">H8472</a>, <a href=\"#/H8473\">H8473</a>, <a href=\"#/H8476\">H8476</a>, <a href=\"#/H8477\">H8477</a>"}]}